snippet.title: First Impressions on Cyberpunk 3776!
snippet.description:
Watch me play Cyberpunk 3776 for the first time! It's a shoot them up indie game. In a cyber-punk-ish atmosphere.
You can check out the game here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/343170/

I do not recommend the game for its pricetag.

Add me on twitter: @gamingb47
